beer.beer_description:
Strata/Ekuanot Cryo/Mosaic

We love hazy IPA’s but sometimes we want something dry and bitter, something like a solid old school WCIPA, but juicy…. and we were always told the grass was greener on the other side.

Inspired by some of our favourite West Coast Haze producers we pushed our interpretation all the way, no point staying on the fence forever. Dry, hop forward with a soft mouthfeel and proper bitterness.
